This program shows the assembler realization for accessing global
data from PIC.

The following pseudo-instruction is used:
.ldgot	<got>		load register <got> with the address of the GOT

showo: Explore how .ldgot and the variable access are implemented.
showx: Look at the resulting executable.
runlo: Run the program at its link address.
runhi: Run the program at some location above its link address.
